Re: Warning : Check your system ( Help me )

Bitcointalk

2010-09-05 23:36:20 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Any suggestions for better text to put for this error message so the
   next person will be less likely to be confused?
   Itʼs trying to tell them their clock is wrong and they need to correct
   it.
   Itʼs relying on 3 time sources:
   1) the system clock
   2) the other nodes, if within an hour of the system clock
   if those disagree, then
   3) the user (asking the user to fix the system clock)
   Iʼve thought about NTP, but this is more secure.
